OL,3,CBuffy The Vampire Slayer actor
OL,4,CNicholas Brendon dies at 54
OL,6,FNicholas Brendon, best known for
OL,7,Fplaying Xander on Buffy The Vampire
OL,8,FSlayer, has died at age 54.
OL,10,FHis family announced on social media
OL,11,Fon Friday the US actor had died in his
OL,12,Fsleep.
OL,14,F"We are heartbroken to share the
OL,15,Fpassing of our brother and son,
OL,16,FNicholas Brendon. He passed in his
OL,17,Fsleep of natural causes," they wrote
OL,18,Falongside photos of Brendon through
OL,19,Fthe years.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@YO]
