OL,3,CBuffy The Vampire Slayer actor
OL,4,CNicholas Brendon dies at 54
OL,6,F"Most people know Nicky for his work
OL,7,Fas an actor and for the characters he
OL,8,Fbrought to life over the years. In
OL,9,Frecent years Nicky has found his
OL,10,Fpassion in painting and art.
OL,12,F"Nicky loved to share his enthusiastic
OL,13,Ftalent with his family, friends and
OL,14,Ffans. He was passionate, sensitive,
OL,15,Fand endlessly driven to create. Those
OL,16,Fwho truly knew him understood that his
OL,17,Fart was one of the purest reflections
OL,18,Fof who he was."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@OO]
