OL,3,CBuffy The Vampire Slayer actor
OL,4,CNicholas Brendon dies at 54
OL,6,FBrendon rose to fame as Xander Harris,
OL,7,Fthe loyal best friend of Sarah
OL,8,FMichelle Gellar's Buffy Summers and
OL,9,FWillow Rosenberg, played by Alyson
OL,10,FHannigan, on Joss Whedon's cult
OL,11,Fseries, which aired from 1997 to 2003.
OL,13,FHannigan paid tribute by sharing a
OL,14,Fphoto of the pair from the show,
OL,15,Fwriting: "My Sweet Nicky, thank you
OL,16,Ffor years of laughter, love and
OL,17,FDodgers. I will think of you every
OL,18,Ftime I see a rocking chair. I love
OL,19,Fyou. RIP."
OL,26,@wD@JOU{D@JO]
