OL,3,CBuffy The Vampire Slayer actor
OL,4,CNicholas Brendon dies at 54
OL,6,FEmma Caulfield, who played former
OL,7,Fdemon Anya Jenkins ` Brendon's on-
OL,8,Fagain, off-again love interest on the
OL,9,Fshow ` shared a video of the actor on
OL,10,Fher Instagram stories in tribute,
OL,11,Falongside a broken heart emoji and the
OL,12,Fcaption: "I love you Nicky."
OL,14,FAfter Buffy The Vampire Slayer ended,
OL,15,FBrendon had recurring roles as cyber
OL,16,Fexpert Kevin Lynch on seven seasons of
OL,17,FCriminal Minds and appeared on Private
OL,18,FPractice.
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@\O]
