OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774260876
OL,3,CBuffy The Vampire Slayer actor
OL,4,CNicholas Brendon dies at 54
OL,6,FHis family added: "While it's no
OL,7,Fsecret that Nicholas had struggles in
OL,8,Fthe past, he was on medications and
OL,9,Ftreatment to manage his diagnosis and
OL,10,Fhe was optimistic about the future at
OL,11,Fthe time of his passing.
OL,13,F"Our family asks for privacy during
OL,14,Fthis time as we grieve his loss and
OL,15,Fcelebrate the life of a man who lived
OL,16,Fwith intensity, imagination, and
OL,17,Fheart. Thank you to everyone who has
OL,18,Fshown love and support."
OL,26,@nD@SOUuD@AOUzD@XO]
